author: ggregory
msg: Rename "encapsulator" to "quoteChar" so we have quoteChar and quotePolicy. Encapsulator makes me want to ask "encapsulate what"? fieldEncapsulator would be better but so verbose, quoteChar feels more to the point to me and provides symmetry with quotePolicy.
